’Щ@79342c01effacef3ee323595f982bd2c27fdd8e6be0f3f3eafc356f982f4945eЪMTitle: title: bytes build
Path: Examples
Content:
Builds binary data from 0x
[
01 02
]
, 0x
[
03
]
, 0x
[
04
]
.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> bytes build 0x[01 02] 0x[03] 0x[04]
Length: 4 (0x4) bytes | null_char printable whitespace ascii_other non_ascii
00000000:   01 02 03 04                                          вЂўвЂўвЂўвЂў


```
Builds binary data from byte numbers.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> bytes build 255 254 253 252
Length: 4 (0x4) bytes | null_char printable whitespace ascii_other non_ascii
00000000:   ff fe fd fc                                          Г—Г—Г—Г—


```
